00:00:58.640 --> 00:00:59.480
Felly, dyna beth rydym ni wedi'i wneud.

00:00:59.480 --> 00:01:01.440
Felly, fe wnaethon yn ffysicol,

00:01:01.440 --> 00:01:02.600
